{{see|Spanish wine}}
Spain is the biggest exporter of wine in the world.<ref>Jessica Jones, [http://www.thelocal.es/20150303/spain-is-worlds-biggest-wine-exporter Spain outstrips France and Italy in wine exports] ''The Local'' 3 March 2015 </ref>

==Automobiles==
{{main|Automotive industry in Spain}}
In 2015 [[Spain]] produced 2.7 million cars, which made it the 8th largest automobile producer country in the world.<ref name="Car Makers Pour">Victor Méndez-Barreira, [https://www.wsj.com/articles/car-makers-pour-money-into-spain-1470613487 Car Makers Pour Money Into Spain],  ''[[Wall Street Journal]], Aug. 7, 2016''</ref> The forecast as of 2016 was to produce a total of 2.8 million vehicles, from which about 80% is for export.<ref name="Car Makers Pour" /> 

